OCC:OKIE DOKIE

   GALVATRON FLIPPED AROUND THE ROOM. DODGEING THE SHOTS AS HE WENT. HIS 
DAMGAE WAS GETTING BETTER DUE TO THE HEALING BUT HE NEED THE ENERGON BLOOD 
FOR IT TO WORK AS WELL AS HE HAD SEEN. HIS HEALING WAS QUICKENED BUT NOT 
NEARLY FAST ENOUGH SAU IF HE WAS SHOT THROUGH THE STOMACH. HE WOULD FIGURE IT 
OUT LATER. HE SENT A COMM"DO YOU HAVE ANY FIGHTING DROIDS IN THIS LITTLE ROOM 
I CAN FIGHT WITH?"
